-Generates optimal planting layout

#############
# Structure #
#############
index.html
-collects state, city, season, plot size, and list of plants
select_plants.html
-user selects plants from a list of avaliable plants
generate.html
-returns the generated optimal plan


Flask based webapp
to run virutalenv
$source env/bin/activate

to create new DB
-run creatdbs.py

